that with my status as the daughter of a minister,

38
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:35,439
my father would surely protect me.

39
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,599
You admitted it before,

40
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,960
but now you're denying it.

41
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,560
You wanted to use me

42
