to get back at your lover.

43
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,800
Do you think I'm a fool?

44
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,520
I was blinded for a moment.

45
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,120
and made a wrong decision.

46
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:01,599
Now,

47
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,000
it's not too late to set things right.

48
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,800
If what I say is true,

49
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,840
can you afford to take the risk?

50
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:10,080
The enemy gets away with it,

51
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,520
