than let one go.

56
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,719
Yesterday's cause

57
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,039
Today's fruit...

58
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,800
Even if you talk a good game,

59
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,879
I won't believe a word of it.

60
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,039
The mission has already departed.

61
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:56,080
Soon,

62
