134
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,680
I love you so much,

135
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,160
but you've let me down.

136
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,800
I'm telling you,

137
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:34,080
if you don't cut ties with that courtesan,

138
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,120
