145
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,759
and never betray the deep affection in the mortal world.

146
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,200
When you had children for me

147
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,519
and managed the household affairs,

148
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:15,000
you said you would only love me in this life,

149
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,960
and never betray me.

150
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,639
Now, just three years later,

151
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,320
staying at the Zuige Pavilion every night,

152
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,960
yet he refuses to look at me.

153
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:22,879
My dear,

154
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:24,799
your heart

155
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,840
is so cruel.

156
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:30,720
My dear,

157
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,519
