158
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,240
Hush,

159
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,039
stop it.

160
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:37,200
The dancers at the Zuige Pavilion

161
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,080
can't compare to you.

162
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,279
Tell me,

163
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,600
what exactly do you want?

164
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,759
It's always pleasant

165
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,080
to talk to a smart person.

166
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,919
I can't find any evidence now,

167
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:01,360
but Gu Hengyuan is definitely not innocent.

168
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:03,639
If you want to avenge your dead lover,

169
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,360
you can't just target me.

170
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:08,000
Even if

171
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,600
I and Gu Hengyuan

172
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:10,600
are accomplices,

173
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:11,200
and co-conspirators,

174
