175
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:16,159
If we hadn't colluded,

176
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,799
he wouldn't have distracted the stableman,

177
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,440
and there wouldn't have been

178
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:20,399
the incident of

179
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,679
