to seek justice without evidence.

197
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:13,039
But I'm so eager

198
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:15,399
to see the bad guy get his comeuppance.

199
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:17,240
Can you

200
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,240
help me?
